ibut that time hasn't been long enough to establish a deep work		gopher.black	70
iflow. I've set aside days of the week for it like Bimodal, but		gopher.black	70
irarely with the isolation necessary to really dig in. Occasionally		gopher.black	70
iI'm successful, but I think it's more to do with luck, or		gopher.black	70
ia motivation I happened to find that day, than any deliberatet		gopher.black	70
iplanning.		gopher.black	70
